history.content:
Now that our info-sessions are over, it's time to welcome you to our WxM family! We will be hosting our first WxM event of the Fall on Monday, 9/14, from 6-8pm! For fun introductions, games, raffles, prizes, and much more join us at our Welcome Event!!!!

No sign up necessary, hope to see you there!

Zoom: https://berkeley.zoom.us/j/92991501018?pwd=bXJjOHpPVmYzeE5nc2psVnBkRUVIdz09

Learn more about us:
Facebook: www.facebook.com/WIMatUCB/
Instagram: @ucbwim
LinkedIn : https://www.linkedin.com/company/womxn-in-mathematics
Visit our website: www.wim.berkeley.edu
Join our Mailing List and Slack: https://tinyurl.com/WxM-2020
